columns.name: key_name
columns.description: The name of the key pair

columns.name: key_pair_id
columns.description: The ID of the key pair

columns.name: key_fingerprint
columns.description: If key pair was created using CreateKeyPair, this is the SHA-1 digest of the DER encoded private key. If key pair was created using ImportKeyPair to provide AWS the public key, this is the MD5 public key fingerprint as specified in section 4 of RFC4716

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: A list of tags assigned to the key pair

columns.name: create_time
columns.description: The time that the keypair was created or imported
